headline: Chubb Limited Announces Pricing of $1.25 Billion Senior Notes Offering by Subsidiary
summary: Chubb Limited (NYSE: CB) announced today that its subsidiary, Chubb INA Holdings LLC, has priced a public offering of $1.25 billion of 4.90% senior notes due 2035 (the "Notes"). The Notes are guaranteed by Chubb Limited.
